name: Dimension Drifter #001
description:
Dimension Drifter is a series of uniqe artworks exploring fantastical beings out of this world

Once worshipped as a deity, they spent their time listening to the prayers and thoughts of the beings around them. The whispers have long been silenced though and they wander around, desperate to hear others once again. They are life and death, growth and destruction. Flowers and plants sprout under their feet, but everything they touch crumbles to ashes. 
They are change. And the change they became. Now they are the one praying, praying for others to be healthy, praying for others to be heard. What use is the loudest voice if noone is there to hear it?  The silence is death but they will not give up. They will continue to wander around, listening. Searching.
